text: Szegedi Egységes Oktatási Labdarúgó Sport Club, commonly known as SZEOL SC, is a Hungarian association football club from the town of Szeged. ==History== Szegedi Egységes Oktatási Labdarúgó SC debuted in the 2016–17 Nemzeti Bajnokság II season of the Hungarian League. ==Managers== * Zoran Kuntić == References == ==External links== * * Profile on Magyar Futball Category:Sport in Szeged Category:Football clubs in Hungary Category:1904 establishments in Hungary
